  "subject": "vCPE BRG allottedResourceRole is null",
  "commit_message": "vCPE BRG allottedResourceRole is null\n\nIn Beijing we used:\no.getNfRole()\n\nIn Casablanca, it was:\no.getTargetNetworkRole()\n\nI'm changing it to:\no.getTargetNetworkRole() != null ? o.getTargetNetworkRole() : o.getNfRole()\n\nChange-Id: I874b2f01fd651bb38a361fa9c36f9937b1f02b2f\nIssue-ID: SO-1200\nSigned-off-by: Rob Daugherty <rd472p@att.com>\n",
